file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: API docs
  description: API 문서
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: https://cabi.42cadet.kr
paths:
  $ref: "./path.yaml"

components:
  parameters: null
  schemas:
    Error:
      type: object
      properties:
        success:
          type: boolean
        message:
          type: string
    Success:
      type: object
      properties:
        success:
          type: boolean
        message:
          type: string
    cabinetList:
      type: object
      required:
        - location
        - floor
        - section
        - cabinet
      properties:
        location:
          type: Array<string>
          example: ["serom", "maru"]
        floor:
          type: Array<Array<integer>>
          # example: [[2, 4, 5], [1]]
        section:
          type: Array<Array<Array<string>>>
          # example: [[['oasis', 'c2'],['c1', 'c2']]]
        cabinet:
          type: Array<Array<Array<Array<cabinetInfo>>>>
          # example: [[[['serom, 2f, oasis cabinetList'], ['serom 2f, c2 cabinetList']], [[serom 4f c1 cabinetList]]]]
    lentInfo:
      type: object
      required:
        - lent_id
        - lent_cabinet_id
        - lent_user_id
        - lent_time
        - expire_time
        - extension
        - intra_id
      properties:
        lent_id:
          type: integer
          example: 1
        lent_cabinet_id:
          type: integer
          example: 1
        lent_user_id:
          type: integer
          example: 1
        lent_time:
          type: string
          example: "2022-01-22"
        expite_time:
          type: string
          example: "2022-02-22"
        extension:
          type: boolean
          example: True
        intra_id:
          type: string
          example: "skim"
    isLent:
      type: object
      required:
        - isLent
      properties:
        isLent:
          type: integer
          exmaple: 1
    lentCabinet:
      type: object
      required:
        - lent_id
        - lent_cabinet_id
        - lent_user_id
        - expire_time
        - extension
        - cabinet_num
        - location
        - floor
        - section
        - activation
      properties:
        lent_id:
          type: integer
          example: 1
        lent_cabinet_id:
          type: integer
          example: 1
        lent_user_id:
          type: integer
          example: 1
        expire_time:
          type: string
          format: datetime
          example: "2021-12-29"
        extension:
          type: boolean
          example: True
        cabinet_num:
          type: integer
          example: 1
        location:
          type: string
          example: "serom"
        floor:
          type: integer
          example: 1
        section:
          type: string
          example: "oasis"
        activation:
          type: boolean
          example: True
    userInfo:
      type: object
      required:
        - user_id
        - intra_id
        - auth
        - email
        - phone
        - access
        - refresh
      properties:
        user_id:
          type: integer
          example: 1
        intra_id:
          type: string
          example: "skim"
        auth:
          type: boolean
          example: True
        email:
          type: string
          example: "skim@student.42seoul.kr"
        phone:
          type: string
          example: "010-0000-0000"
        access:
          type: string
          example: "1389fdsjklfsjkl"
        refresh:
          type: string
          example: "2fjlksdflk02309"

  responses:
    BadRequest:
      description: 잘못된 요청
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/Error"
          example:
            success: false
            message: 잘못된 요청
    InternalServerError:
      description: 서버 에러
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/Error"
          example:
            success: false
            message: 서버 내부 오류
    SuccessResponse:
      description: 요청 성공
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/Success"
          example:
            success: true
            message: 요청 성공

Error:
unmarshal: yaml: unmarshal errors:
  yaml: line 1: cannot unmarshal !!str `./path....` into ogen.PathItem
